Ulario login help
-----------------

Logging in allows you to identify yourself using a previously created
account.

You can register a new account using a unique name by supplying a secret
password which will be used to authenticate.

You can connect anonymously as a guest.  You will be unable to speak or
use any commands that can affect other players or the game, but you will
be free to access all public information.

You can terminates your connection.  You will be disconnected
automatically if you do not either login or register within 60 seconds.
